Ecuador throws its support behind Peru in their demands for the return of over 40,000 Machu Picchu artifacts taken by US explorer Hiram Bingham III, and now in Yale's possession. (Reuters)President Herman Van Rompuy predicts the possible collapse of the European Union but then says "I'm very confident we will overcome this". (The Guardian)A nationwide strike takes place in Bangladesh after former Prime Minister Khaleda Zia was evicted from her home. (Al Jazeera) (Hindustan Times)